      <title>墨西哥大选后，AMLO 推出医疗诊所资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/amlo-rolls-out-health-clinic-funding-following-mexico-s-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔周二宣布了一项加强墨西哥医疗保健的计划，旨在解决其政党在选举中取得压倒性胜利后选民对其政府提出的一项关键投诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/amlo-rolls-out-health-clinic-funding-following-mexico-s-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 15:21:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非主要反对党对联合政府抱有乐观态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/south-african-election-main-opposition-sees-room-for-optimism-on-coalition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非主要反对党民主联盟领导人表示，投资者对该党将与非国大达成联合执政协议组建下一届政府的乐观态度没有错，该党愿意进行以国家利益为优先的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/south-african-election-main-opposition-sees-room-for-optimism-on-coalition</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 14:54:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法拉奇在英国竞选活动开始时喝了奶昔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/farage-draws-crowds-to-clacton-and-gets-drenched-in-beverage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国脱欧的策划者奈杰尔·法拉奇在狂欢节般的氛围中发起了竞选克拉克顿议会席位的行动，数百人聚集到埃塞克斯海滨，承诺颠覆英国政治秩序。但并非一切都如这位新任改革英国领袖所愿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/farage-draws-crowds-to-clacton-and-gets-drenched-in-beverage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 14:52:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国议员对瓦根克内西特提起煽动性投诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/german-lawmaker-files-incitement-complaint-against-wagenknecht</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国一名保守党议员已对极左翼德国社会主义运动党 (BSW) 党员萨拉·瓦根克内西特 (Sahra Wagenknecht) 提起法律诉讼，指控她在上个月的竞选集会上对他发表的言论构成煽动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/german-lawmaker-files-incitement-complaint-against-wagenknecht</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 14:38:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>这些是决定莫迪未来的印度王者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/here-are-the-india-kingmakers-who-will-determine-modi-s-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在印度大选中未能获得多数票后，纳伦德拉·莫迪的未来现在掌握在两个出了名的不可靠的盟友手中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/here-are-the-india-kingmakers-who-will-determine-modi-s-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 14:22:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称有理由质疑内塔尼亚胡延长加沙战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/biden-every-reason-to-question-if-netanyahu-prolonging-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登在周二接受《时代》杂志采访时表示，人们有理由得出这样的结论：以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡延长加沙战争是出于他自己的政治考虑，并且不排除派遣美军保卫台湾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/biden-every-reason-to-question-if-netanyahu-prolonging-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 13:32:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司首席执行官反对日益增长的孤立主义言论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/boeing-ceo-warns-isolation-will-hurt-trade-as-us-election-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国准备迎接关键的总统选举之际，波音公司首席执行官警告称，美国转向孤立主义将阻碍出口并损害经济，并反对保护主义言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/boeing-ceo-warns-isolation-will-hurt-trade-as-us-election-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 13:14:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪誓言即使失去印度多数席位仍将保住权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/modi-poised-to-lose-india-majority-need-allies-to-keep-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管纳伦德拉·莫迪的政党在议会中失去多数席位，但他仍誓言继续担任印度总理，这迫使他自十年前上台以来首次依靠盟友组建政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/modi-poised-to-lose-india-majority-need-allies-to-keep-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 11:54:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称乌克兰问题计划获支持 峰会受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/china-says-its-ukraine-plan-is-winning-support-after-summit-snub</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最高外交官表示，已有二十多个国家表示支持北京解决俄乌冲突的愿景。几天前，中国表示将不参加即将在瑞士举行的和平峰会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/china-says-its-ukraine-plan-is-winning-support-after-summit-snub</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 11:07:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸影子政府预示经济动荡加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/myanmar-s-shadow-government-flags-deepening-economic-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸影子民族团结政府的估计显示，缅甸货币暴跌、美元储备大幅减少以及通货膨胀飙升，正使缅甸经济陷入更深的危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/myanmar-s-shadow-government-flags-deepening-economic-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 09:41:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
